					</div>
					<div class="span4 i-block">
						<h3>Best Prices Widget </h3>
						<p>For Publishers - Show the best prices of the product discussed in that page. If you are writing a review about a product, you can include this widget to show the best prices for that product from leading stores in India inside that page itself. <a href="#features" style="color: gray;font-style: italic;font-size: 12px;">More Details</a></p>
